profile: Beatnik & Mod Inc. is a creative, modern flooring and renovation shop, located just minutes from Deerfoot Trail in SE Calgary. Our showroom is inviting and not overwhelming and we offer FREE no-obligation estimates.

profile:
Located in Airdrie Chateau Flooring has been Servicing Airdrie, Calgary and surrounding areas for over 5 years and we believe excellent customer service is the key.

We have expertly trained staff to assist, educate and help you to choose the right products for your space, our installation crews are experienced and professional who make sure the fit and finish of the completed project are unsurpassed. Combine this expertise with longstanding relationships with our trade partners and sub trades, the result is consistent and excellent workmanship. We look forward to helping you with your flooring projects.
